{"tid":988584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] 震驚！唐詩詠認有追求者：唔講得","createTime":"2019-01-20T08:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T09:32:10.000Z","uid":82917,"like":38,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca082492ad740c6376981f98fd669f1a3de201d","tid":988584,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唐詩詠認有追求者</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唐詩詠認有追求者</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唐詩詠認有追求者</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0tAUqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0tAUqf.png&h=0bb53400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不想活了！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n邊條水魚咁大諗頭肯哽左我姨？睇完篇新聞小美忍唔住喊到失禁，家陣跪左係屎塔隔離痛哭流涕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 面對即將出嫁的姨感到悲痛萬分！經過唐姨狙擊手小美同吉妹鑑定後，鎖定水魚有兩條！分別係表哥前男友 &mdash; 的士邦（鄭子邦），及被記者戲稱 &mdash; 四眼吳卓羲（陳思銘）。我真係恭喜你地呀！溝到個唐姨咁好既絕。。。絕世閪女人，快撚啲娶埋佢添呀，唔係溝嚟把撚呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctd1P17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fctd1P17.png&h=6f34cb30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">鄭子邦</span></span><br />\n唐詩詠承認有圈外人追求，「唔講得！講咗無㗎喇」。她希望新一年多點工作，最想拍一部動作片挑戰難度，「女人要努力搵錢，愛情有就有，無都有錢嘛！有無愛情都要搵錢，這個是我的目標」。被指與姚子羚舊愛鄭子邦一起做義工，疑似展開新戀情？她說：「我以為單身好正，點知單身後身邊所有男性都變了我的伴侶，我也要跟他們講聲不好意思；其實當時有近20個義工，我不希望今次說是他，下次又說是其他人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/275703/%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0%E6%96%B0%E6%88%80%E6%83%85%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E6%9C%89%E7%9D%80%E8%90%BD-%E8%A2%AB%E5%BD%B1%E5%88%B0%E5%AD%96%E4%BD%8F%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E9%84%AD%E5%AD%90%E9%82%A6%E9%BD%8A%E5%81%9A%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F275703%2F%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%25A9%25A0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2588%2580%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259D%2580%25E8%2590%25BD-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25AD%2596%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2582%25A6%25E9%25BD%258A%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=96471fe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/275703/%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0%E6%96%B0%E6%88%80%E6%83%85%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E6%9C%89%E7%9D%80%E8%90%BD-%E8%A2%AB%E5%BD%B1%E5%88%B0%E5%AD%96%E4%BD%8F%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E9%84%AD%E5%AD%90%E9%82%A6%E9%BD%8A%E5%81%9A%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n同場的唐詩詠則否認與姚子羚的前男友鄭子邦拍拖，她強調和對方是一班人齊做義工，將來的事就不會評論，並承認現有圈外人追求，但拒透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ent/729400/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F729400%2F&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a8a11568\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F729400%2F&h=d9e7012a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ent/729400/</a><br />\n<br />\n提到早前她表示有位圈外追求者，小心翼翼護愛苗的她強調對方是「朋友」，並澄清早前在社交網站貼圖、被解讀為暗示今年結婚是誤會，但她會努力，不排除閃婚，又謂與「朋友」「食吓飯先」已是好開始，今次開新劇預計要5個月時間，正好是一場試練，看對方能否接受自己的時間表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2F&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=77d372c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2F&h=08f6d07d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">吳卓羲（四眼）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/20/154948_7b951debba2c07f8bee3e78d15afe71b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F20%2F154948_7b951debba2c07f8bee3e78d15afe71b.png&h=95c61849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.modia.com.hk/2018/11/16/106565/%E3%80%8C%E5%9B%9B%E7%9C%BC%E5%90%B3%E5%8D%93%E7%BE%B2%E3%80%8Dsweet%E7%88%86%E6%91%B8%E9%A0%AD-%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0%EF%BC%9A%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F%E5%92%97%E4%B9%8B%E5%98%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2018%2F11%2F16%2F106565%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%258D%2593%25E7%25BE%25B2%25E3%2580%258Dsweet%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2591%25B8%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%25A9%25A0%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E7%25B3%259F%25E5%2592%2597%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2598%259B%2F&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b002909c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.modia.com.hk/2018/11/16/106565/%E3%80%8C%E5%9B%9B%E7%9C%BC%E5%90%B3%E5%8D%93%E7%BE%B2%E3%80%8Dsweet%E7%88%86%E6%91%B8%E9%A0%AD-%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0%EF%BC%9A%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F%E5%92%97%E4%B9%8B%E5%98%9B/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日《蘋果》就聯絡到Samuel，問係咪同詩詠拍拖？佢以短訊回覆﹕「It was really just a dinner with friends.(我只係同朋友食飯)。」問到覺得詩詠係咪好女仔，會否展開追求？佢答：「I don&rsquo;t know her enough to comment. As a friend, she is great. That&rsquo;s all I can say.thank you.(我對佢所知不多。作為一個朋友，佢好好，呢個係我唯一可以講，多謝)」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E5%9B%9B%E7%9C%BC%E5%90%B3%E5%8D%93%E7%BE%B2%E3%80%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%87%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B-samuel%E8%AE%9A%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9-082030542.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%258D%2593%25E7%25BE%25B2%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%2589%258B-samuel%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%25A9%25A9-082030542.html&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a629944c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E5%9B%9B%E7%9C%BC%E5%90%B3%E5%8D%93%E7%BE%B2%E3%80%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%87%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B-samuel%E8%AE%9A%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9-082030542.html</a><br />\n<br />\n讀者話唔知呢個係咪唐詩詠新男友，最初係詩詠同林子萱先到餐廳，大約過咗一個鐘左右，「四眼吳卓羲」就現身，聽到詩詠向林子萱介紹「四眼吳卓羲」叫Samuel，其間林子萱離開張枱，佢哋即刻變得好sweet，久唔久仲深情對望，傾到興起仲見到「四眼吳卓羲」摸一摸詩詠個頭，冇耐又見到搭住詩詠嘅膊頭，最後由「四眼吳卓羲」埋單，好有風度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/hit/realtime/article/20181116/58917702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fhit%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F58917702&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7fba86ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fhit%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F58917702&h=c3b84349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/hit/realtime/article/20181116/58917702</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1811a12f99ec607e729c6f584ce3b60cacb568","tid":988584,"uid":82917,"like":40,"dislike":4,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">好姊妹疑暗指屍詠蜜運中！並發老姣回應：你兩個...</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vue8vdM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVue8vdM.png&h=3a29b070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩！講到似層層咁喎，慌死有路頂啦呢鋪！一經狙擊手吉野妹極速起底後發現，原來無料到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎呢段三角戀已萌芽多時，未知姨最於會情歸何處？定係無疾而終？有待日後於兩人IG上揭曉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4UXotJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4UXotJ.png&h=35e50dde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BgRCotL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgRCotL.png&h=970ff267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>妄想一天你們會散，會選美嗎？</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nsize=6]經典重溫[/size=6]<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唐姨：新聞無得自己煲的！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nn0LxpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNn0LxpV.png&h=181b898d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唐詩詠自與洪永城分後一直單身。不過她早前在Instagram上，貼出上載有自己、黃翠如、C君未婚妻黃天頤，以及一位圈外朋友的照片，並留言說：「下年（今年）呢個時候，就變成有3位可愛人妻。」隨即爆出唐詩詠有意於今年結婚的消息！<br />\n<br />\n她星期五在銅鑼灣出席商場迎新春揭幕禮時，就笑言大家都誤會了：「圈外朋友結了婚，第二個是翠如，第三個就是天頤，不是我，我會努力。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n挑那星！連結婚都要自爆煲新聞，唔係真係有人埋單就收嗲啦。成日有意無意提到自己內心有幾咁恨嫁，醜唔醜呀你？又要捆綁式拉埋脆魚同你煲新聞齊齊上C1，緊係啦，好姊妹分鳩同味！殿堂級視后真係唔話得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQeo3uc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQeo3uc.png&h=f9a45d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑒於我姨年事已高，奉勸兩位城中型男埋單趁早！有望早日遠離永城！冥得如意郎君！恭喜恭喜！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C0n2zAT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC0n2zAT.png&h=5a093121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd0f6016ad28b0b27e6d1400cbff85bcc7e656a5","tid":988584,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"表哥嚟"},{"pid":"ba149880a1183c10d0c11dacf67eefe5937b7fb0","tid":988584,"uid":82917,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gV6yGon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgV6yGon.png&h=2cfa6e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>不 能 錯 過 的 <br />\n絕 世 好 女 友</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/105238_05da613cc9cf1db9565eef117d9a7212.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F105238_05da613cc9cf1db9565eef117d9a7212.png&h=945be42e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/105241_5f46980a871c9a8b93fc700c4619982a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F105241_5f46980a871c9a8b93fc700c4619982a.png&h=47239d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/105246_2b5028ad8d884bb837b714600203b207.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F105246_2b5028ad8d884bb837b714600203b207.png&h=7a67d2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gi